node.text:
We are announcing Community Challenges. Here comes the first one: «Standard Bearer».
— Drop to any map in the Capture mode.
— Carry the enemy flag for 30 seconds outside the bases on a map.
— Win the match
Additional mission:
— Kill 3+ enemies
⠀
Rewards:
Top 10 participant will get 300 gems, plus 1000 coins if additional mission is complete.
⠀
How to participate:
1. Record your successful game
2. Upload the video to YouTube. It MUST have the following name «Pixel Gun 3D Standard Bearer Challenge»
3. Max one entry per player.
4. We will stop submissions on Monday, August 12.
***
In this video you can see how one of the devs, desperaterussian, completes this challenge.
Aaaand, yeah, remember, those, who complete the mission faster than others will definitely receive the prize.
Good luck!
⠀
#PixelGun3D #pg3d #pixelgun

We found four more suspects in this tangled case. You can see their faces in the picture 🦹‍♂️

⚠️WARNING⚠️ These dangerous criminals hacked into our secret servers and stole valuable data - a piece of code, without which the game can not exist 🤯

We're announcing a reward for 10 players who will decipher the full piece of code – 💎 1000 GEMS!

Your task is to:
1️⃣ Find the stolen letters in the last videos of these criminals;
2️⃣ Make a phrase out of them;
3️⃣ Send it to us via Google Forms.

We've figured out 4 of them, but rumor has it there's more of them... So we are continuing our investigation and will be sure to let you know as soon as we find the rest of the bad guys😈

🚨We'll also post the form as soon as we find the remaining members of this gang🚨

Good luck, detectives. Together we will save Pixel Gun 3D! 💪

#pg3d #pixelgun #pixelgun3d

node.text:
The first issue of the New-Blockcisco Times is on all newsstands! We have only the most up-to-date news from the city and its surroundings 📰

IS THIS AN INVASION? 🙀
The other day in the Wasteland, among the sand dunes, scientists discovered a strange creature. Surprisingly, it is most likely a Worm! Even more surprising is its colossal size. You can appreciate it from the photos from the scene.

As horrible as this worm looks, our correspondent assures us that this creature is more cute than dangerous. However, we still recommend not to feed it from the hands (Editor's note)

Is the appearance of this worm connected with a nearby toxic dump? That's what we'll find out in the next journalistic investigation by our special correspondent, Pixel Cobe.

EVENING IN NEW-BLOCKCISCO 🌆
Who would have thought that the sun would set in our sunny little town (by the way, the sunniest on the east coast of the pixel continent)? Well, we didn't expect that either!

We took a comment from Professor Stone, a renowned scientist, member of the Academy of Pixel Science, and the chief technical genius of Advanced Mining Corporation. According to him, "The origins and causes of this phenomenon are unknown, and our prospects for a happy future are hazy.

We were unable to unravel the meaning of this philosophical statement. We can only guess whether it leads to irreversible climate change and apocalypse or whether it is a harmless joke of Mother Nature...

NOW THE CITY IS SAFE 🚒
This week, after 15 years of construction, a real Fire Station opened in New-Blockcisco! Now we can definitely be considered a megalopolis.

Even the mayor himself was present at the opening ceremony. He assured that now the city can fear neither fires nor the invasion of giant fire-breathing monsters from the depths of the sea. 

However, the most pressing question at the opening ceremony was the cost of building the Fire Station. It was rumored to be about a million diamonds. The mayor, as always, refrained from commenting.

#pg3d #pixelgun #pixelgun3d
